fields.name: heapIdx
fields.comment: The index in the PathHeap. -1 if not assigned.

fields.name: g
fields.comment: The total cost of all path points up to this one. Corresponds to the A* g-score.

fields.name: h
fields.comment: The estimated cost from this path point to the target. Corresponds to the A* h-score.

fields.name: costMalus
fields.comment: The additional cost of the path point. If negative, the path point will be sorted out by NodeProcessors.

fields.name: bestNode
fields.comment: The nearest path point of the path that is constructed
